    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, what do you mean by \"goblin glue\" and \"flexible goblins\"? I'm just talking about structural engineering materials. Can you just explain the physics of the tensile strength part without the weird metaphors?",
      "source": "evaluator"
